Package net.sf.ehcache.transaction.manager

This package temporarily contains Bitronix stuff.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
TransactionManagerLookup Interface to enable a XA transactional cache to access the JTA TransactionManager.
 

Class Summary
DefaultTransactionManagerLookup Default TransactionManagerLookup implementation, that will be used by an initializing Cache should the user have not specified otherwise.
